data.description: Come check out this pristine 3 bedroom - 2.5 bath Chatham model in much desired Kings Croft!  This spacious unit has been freshly painted throughout and features a sunken living room with a corner wood burning fireplace, a formal dining room, and a large eat-in kitchen with updated floors and granite countertops along with pendant lighting, a center island and full appliance package.  Newer sliding glass door leads to patio area great for family get togethers.  The master suite has a huge walk-in closet, full bathroom along with a stand alone make-up station in the separate dressing area.  Two other nice sized bedrooms with full bath and laundry room upstairs.  Don't forget about the fully finished basement with a great room and office in addition to a utility room and additional storage space.  Newer heater and air conditioner, newer laminate wood floors, newer dishwasher, and newer washer/dryer.  Kings Croft is a sought after community that has on site management, is extremely well maintained, super convenient to major commuter routes, shopping, dining, proximity to Philly, the new Lifetime Fitness Center, and let's not forget the renowned Cherry Hill Twp schools. All exterior maintenance is taken care of for you and your water usage is included as well. This unit is sparkling and will not last long!
